Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------OPCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:51.61,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}该如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:56.31,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}虽说是平日理所当然的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.14,0:01:00.00,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}真是复杂呐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.34,0:01:03.00,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}快乐的时候欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.19,0:01:07.44,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}喜欢的时候只是要歌唱而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:10.47,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但是却
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.69,0:01:15.99,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}总有一天愿望会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.64,0:01:19.68,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但是「总有一天」是哪一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:23.45,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}已经等不及了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.65,0:01:26.23,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在1  2  3的信号之后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.37,0:01:28.88,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}展开双手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.16,0:01:34.44,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}用全身去集满阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.58,0:01:37.11,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}会在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:40.59,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}请告诉我我力所能及的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.76,0:01:46.15,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}尽情地受伤  尽情地奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.35,0:01:53.19,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}数十次地摔倒哭泣  即使这样还是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.47,0:01:57.32,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}令人叹服般地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.83,0:02:01.85,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}相信着明天
