Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.07,0:02:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脏…脏了也不要紧  猪尾吕义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.54,0:02:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨一定会帮你洗干净的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧才怪  那样不就全身湿透了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…清花老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是要去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去小鸠的家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:03:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是但是…可以住在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊  只要小鸠你喜欢的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.48,0:03:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是我的朋友  也是这栋公寓的管理员  千岁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面  我叫花户小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠小姐是吗  初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫三原千岁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.24,0:03:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什么不懂的或是不便的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.57,0:03:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尽管对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千岁  之后就麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回托儿所了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿我就过去帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是像从前一样总在关心别人呢  清花她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.64,0:03:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去好善良的人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该说「从今天起要承蒙您的照顾了」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天起我会照顾您的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫花户小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你照顾她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行李要几点送过来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有这些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…没有被子什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…那我这就带你去房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这公寓真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这房间好棒啊  猪尾吕义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪尾吕义先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.31,0:04:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土…鸠…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然敢把我丢在一边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:05:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了吧  我在这里是布娃娃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该去托儿所了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不快点…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要迟到啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事  话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.21,0:05:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这娃娃是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊  搞得你一身泥水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个可爱的娃娃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  这样就干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她比你机灵多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房间怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有屋顶  可以滚来滚去  棒极了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在打扫卫生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.43,0:06:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.77,0:06:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  那我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  那我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着连公寓都帮她介绍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…可是那孩子来了以后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以欺负她哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想吃几次苦头啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在对任何人都警惕一点比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨停了真好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且明天托儿所休息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加油收集金平糖啊  猪尾吕义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「欧式点心  奇洛尔」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还是晴天的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才叫你带伞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子一时半会是不会停了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来只好冒雨前行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分啊  只有你自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有雨伞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.87,0:07:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话  就拿去用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.86,0:07:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本也是给客人用的雨伞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…等雨停了我就还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对小鸠来说  刚才的应答还算得体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就保持这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  来这里收集想被治愈的人的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从某种意义上来说也对…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是人们经常进出的地方嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么情报也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借来的伞没了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被哪个人拿错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:09:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被随便拿走的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？伞是可以随便拿走的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…明明是蛋糕店老板借给我的伞…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？又见面了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伞不见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的伞借给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦  我家就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要是没伞的话  这娃娃也会被淋湿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买这么多零食吃  小心又会变胖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:10:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  桂木你个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不站住的话小心我揍你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.42,0:10:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住也会被你打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋桂木
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有明知自己会淋湿却还借伞给我的人呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.46,0:10:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.31,0:10:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  小鸠小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  脸上有榻榻米的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.09,0:10:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好丢人…脸上竟然有榻榻米的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让千岁小姐乱想的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.03,0:11:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.94,0:11:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的伞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然知道我的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.05,0:11:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  在对借给我伞的蛋糕店老板道歉的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他告诉我绿色水手服是这所学校的校服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要感谢猪尾吕义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪尾吕义先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.13,0:11:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.09,0:11:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指这只布娃娃？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  真是奇怪的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫花户小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫田所睦美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面的头发翘起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  我脸上还有榻榻米的痕迹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话不能算打圆场呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别介意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  我还有晨练
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  刚才的男孩有点坏坏的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.39,0:12:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像藤本先生一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  要是迟到的话又要被欺负了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟到了1分23秒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1…1分？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.15,0:12:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有1分钟  迟到也是迟到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.04,0:12:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你肯定是睡到最后一刻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榻榻米的痕迹已经消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从被子里滚出来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有被子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被藤本说了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点粗鲁  但他可不是坏孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.19,0:13:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果被欺负了的话就告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.59,0:13:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你给他施拳头之刑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.67,0:13:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳…拳头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  就像以前一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.18,0:13:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  难得放晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来晒午睡用的被子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像又要下雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠有伞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.93,0:13:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本有吧  和她一起回去怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接下来有事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的伞拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你合打一把伞我可不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.96,0:13:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合打一把伞？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是指两个人撑一把伞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像清花老师说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的下起雨来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.33,0:14:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿错伞的人把伞还回来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小鸠？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.10,0:14:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又见面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田所睦美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫睦美就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伞回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊  太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睦美又来买东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  剑道部的练习很辛苦  肚子很快就饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.94,0:14:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:15:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为吃太多会发胖…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.22,0:15:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  给
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.08,0:15:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个就是合打一把伞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睦美？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:16:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睦美  很悲伤的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.38,0:16:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做才能让她打起精神来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道  那种事谁都没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.44,0:16:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好  请开门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  很抱歉吵到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面  我是管理员的女儿千帆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是千世
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.05,0:16:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面  我是花户小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有被子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.68,0:16:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  妈妈说不介意的话请你拿去用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说虽然是以前用过的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:16:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到被子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被治愈了怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让睦美重新打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总…总而言之  我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你打算干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是觉得现在让那孩子静一静比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话想对你说  关于睦美的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说  请和睦美也合打一把伞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「也和睦美」是什么意思啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.59,0:18:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.93,0:18:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睦美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.87,0:18:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前些日子…因为睦美露出非常悲伤的表情…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.93,0:18:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你和其他的女孩子合打一把伞的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我才不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我多管闲事的话  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…希望睦美能打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.23,0:19:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  请和睦美合打一把伞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样对之前那女孩不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么嘛  说了不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在和那女孩交往什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.56,0:20:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是因为她说忘了带伞才一起回去的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睦美  来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.63,0:20:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点吧  要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂木  等等啊  我会被淋湿的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.49,0:20:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再往那边去点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太挤了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为就是这样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.75,0:20:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这样说  可伞小…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睦美好像不是很开心的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.58,0:21:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪呢  猪尾吕义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.47,0:21:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.69,0:21:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金平糖多了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.69,0:21:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不就是为了这个才想治愈那个女孩的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想让睦美打起精神来才帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  不管怎么说  这样一来那女孩受伤的心就被治愈了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金平糖增加了就是最好的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.52,0:21:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.14,0:21:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前途堪忧呢  这真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.89,0:22:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的…气息是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.92,0:22:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.21,0:22:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么  秀一郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.62,0:22:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.95,0:22:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次也算是比较顺利  就给你个好分数吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.71,0:22:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.38,0:22:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没事吧  猪尾吕义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.10,0:22:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土·鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.26,0:22:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0分！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.91,0:22:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了  猪尾吕义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.86,0:22:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你明明说要给我个好分数的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让你弄的我满身又是泥又是墨的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.44,0:22:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没关系的  雨一定会帮你洗干净的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.68,0:22:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爷的愤怒是不会被洗掉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.15,0:22:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…
